{"tid":1532217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學校好少人響應罷課 乜撚嘢都做唔撚到屌","createTime":"2019-09-02T12:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:25:37.000Z","uid":312324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2557112758a15ea230fcc650ebbad58dee2f86ec","tid":1532217,"uid":312324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:54:53.000Z","msg":"我間學校罷課就有分兩個時段嘅 點名之前可以集會 唔洗家長信 但唔可以嗌口號 講嘢唔可以用咪 仲有有啲on9 f1蝗蟲老母入黎影相 依段時間都算頗多人 但一到要家長信 就剩返20個以內嘅人罷課 但就有6-7個老師圍住 怕死我哋會搞事咁 有舊生返黎都唔比同我哋講野 傾下計都唔得 話咩怕舊生入面有鬼 我當時真係反曬白眼 再之後有assembly 有人唔入 咁我同班frd就選擇入啦 跟住國歌嘅時候我哋就背住個台 遮右眼 點知比訓導話唔respect個場合......<br />\n所以到頭來 我哋就淨係可以靜坐 完全毫無意義 想做多啲嘢但限制又多 又少人響應 可以點做 唔想聽日都係咁樣9坐當做左嘢 <br />\n好想可以好似其他學校咁 但問題係完全唔夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b972a542c9a6b547bfac997a59abcd17827208","tid":1532217,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:56:45.000Z","msg":"中國國歌同旗根本唔值得respect"},{"pid":"e298dba6aa65adbf514807741bd564182658415d","tid":1532217,"uid":315924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推到江永祥仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n仲有幾個鐘就返學啦好緊張<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cff649c822b191b605659fbd22cd7a929b2aed1e","tid":1532217,"uid":48838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:03:21.000Z","msg":"脫離同溫層，睇吓出面世界係點都好"},{"pid":"8d031bd51e7b15770fd2c6577e9b466fdeb4c371","tid":1532217,"uid":312324,"like":0,"dis